      "id": "frag-002-class",
      "title": "类图设计原则",
      "tags": ["UML", "设计模式", "类图", "SOLID"],
      "nodes": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "content": "类图设计原则"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "content": "类图是面向对象设计的核心图表，遵循 SOLID 原则可提高代码质量。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 3,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "content": "SOLID 原则"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": true,
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "list_item",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "单一职责原则 (SRP)：一个类只负责一项职责"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "list_item",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "开闭原则 (OCP)：对扩展开放，对修改关闭"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "list_item",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "里氏替换原则 (LSP)：子类可以替换父类"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "list_item",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "接口隔离原则 (ISP)：接口职责单一"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "list_item",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "content": "依赖倒置原则 (DIP)：依赖抽象而非具体"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
